public class ClaimSearchCriteria
extends ClaimInfoCriteria
implements java.io.Serializable
    ClaimSearchCriteria Encapsulates the search criteria for a Claim search. The system does not store ClaimSearchCriteria entities, they are exist only for a search and are discarded after use.
